      • vmmRegisterDs

        public int vmmRegisterDs()
        The function deals with the VMM_REGISTER_DS message. It registers the VMM to the DS.
        Returns:
        success status. If the output is 0, the VMM registration is successful.

      • vmmNotifyDs

        public void vmmNotifyDs()
        The function deals with the VMM_NOTIFY_DS message. It notifies the DS about free resource information.

      • asRmNotifyVmm

        public void asRmNotifyVmm(java.io.ObjectInputStream in,
                          java.io.ObjectOutputStream out)
        The function deals with the AS_RM_NOTIFY_VMM message. It receives a message from the AS. According to the type contained in the message, it will suspend or remove a VM.
        Parameters:
        in - ObjectInputStream instance retrieved by the socket.
        out - ObjectOutputStream instance retrieved by the socket.

      • dsVmDeregisterVmm

        public void dsVmDeregisterVmm(java.io.ObjectInputStream in,
                              java.io.ObjectOutputStream out)
        The function deals with the DS_VM_DEREGISTER_VMM message. It receives the message from the DS and removes the VM associated the user Id in the message format.
        Parameters:
        in - ObjectInputStream instance retrieved by the socket.
        out - ObjectOutputStream instance retrieved by the socket.

      • asRmRegisterVmm

        The function deals with the AS_RM_REGISTER_VMM message. It receives the message from the AS and returns the user id to the AS.
        Parameters:
        in - ObjectInputStream instance retrieved by the socket.
        out - ObjectOutputStream instance retrieved by the socket.
